prompts.title: Full Startup Business Blueprint
prompts.description: Extremely detailed business strategy generator
prompts.prompt: Act as a senior business consultant. Create a 10-page comprehensive business plan for a sustainable vertical farming startup in Singapore. Include: Executive Summary, Market Analysis (TAM/SAM/SOM), Cost Structure (CAPEX/OPEX), Marketing Strategy, 3-year Financial Projections, and Risk Mitigation plans. Use professional corporate terminology and data-driven insights.
prompts.trendContext: High demand for AI-driven business planning.

prompts.title: Next.js Fullstack Architecture
prompts.description: In-depth technical software design
prompts.prompt: Design the system architecture for a real-time collaborative whiteboarding app using Next.js 15, Socket.io, Redis for pub/sub, and PostgreSQL with Prisma. Explain the database schema for users, boards, and drawing actions. Detail how to handle horizontal scaling and state synchronization between multiple server instances to prevent data conflicts. Provide a folder structure and key API endpoint definitions.
prompts.trendContext: Essential for developers building complex SaaS platforms.

prompts.title: Epic Fantasy World Lore Book
prompts.description: Massive world-building for novelists
prompts.prompt: Construct a detailed lore guide for a fantasy world called 'Aethelgard' where gravity is controlled by ancient floating crystals. Describe the creation myth involving the 'Core Shapers', the map of the 7 major floating islands, the political tension between the 'Crystal Keepers' and the 'Void Walkers', and the unique magic system based on sound frequencies. Include historical timelines, main deities, and cultural taboos.
prompts.trendContext: Used by authors to generate deep narrative foundations.

prompts.title: 30-Day Viral Content Strategy
prompts.description: Month-long social media execution plan
prompts.prompt: Develop a detailed 30-day content calendar for a tech YouTuber focusing on AI news. For each day, provide: 1. A viral hook title, 2. A primary platform (YouTube, TikTok, or X), 3. A brief script outline or visual description, 4. 5 target hashtags, and 5. A specific call to action (CTA). Ensure the strategy builds momentum leading up to a major product launch on Day 30.
prompts.trendContext: Critical for creators scaling their personal brand.

prompts.title: Legal Contract Review Assistant
prompts.description: Complex analytical legal support
prompts.prompt: Review the following (hypothetical) NDA agreement for a software partnership. Identify potential 'red flag' clauses regarding intellectual property ownership, non-compete duration, and jurisdiction. Suggest 5 specific amendments to better protect the subcontractor's rights while remaining fair to the primary contractor. Use formal legal tone and cite common industry standards.
prompts.trendContext: Growing niche for AI in professional services.

prompts.title: AI Research Paper Summary
prompts.description: Deep academic technical breakdown
prompts.prompt: Deep dive into the 'Attention Is All You Need' paper. Explain the Transformer architecture's Scaled Dot-Product Attention vs Multi-Head Attention mechanism. Break down the positional encoding logic and why it replaced RNNs/LSTMs. Finally, summarize the impact this paper had on LLMs like GPT-4 and Gemini in under 500 words, ensuring technical accuracy for a PhD-level audience.
prompts.trendContext: High interest in understanding the 'under the hood' of AI breakthroughs.
